OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776038571
OL,3,CTyson Fury wins comeback fight against
OL,4,CArslanbek Makhmudov by unanimous
OL,5,Cdecision
OL,7,FTyson Fury made a successful comeback
OL,8,Fby registering an emphatic points
OL,9,Fvictory over Arslanbek Makhmudov at
OL,10,FTottenham Hotspur Stadium on Saturday.
OL,12,FAnthony Joshua watched from ringside
OL,13,Fahead of a potential all-British
OL,14,Fshowdown later this year as Fury
OL,15,Fsecured his first win since defeating
OL,16,FFrancis Ngannou in October 2023.
OL,18,FA dominant display after coming out of
OL,19,Fretirement for the fifth time was
OL,20,Frewarded with scores of 120-108 120-
OL,21,F108 119-109 from the judges.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
