PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776038571
OL,3,CTyson Fury wins comeback fight against
OL,4,CArslanbek Makhmudov by unanimous
OL,5,Cdecision
OL,7,FMakhmudov looked to be tiring as early
OL,8,Fas the fourth round and his
OL,9,Flimitations made him a prime target
OL,10,Ffor Fury after 16 months of
OL,11,Finactivity, providing tough rounds
OL,12,Fwithout ever threatening an upset.
OL,14,FThere was no pomp and ceremony from
OL,15,FMakhmudov as he marched straight into
OL,16,Fthe ring to the sound of an air raid
OL,17,Fsiren.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
