PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776038571
OL,3,CTyson Fury wins comeback fight against
OL,4,CArslanbek Makhmudov by unanimous
OL,5,Cdecision
OL,7,FIn contrast, Fury's entrance for his
OL,8,FNetflix debut began with Blue Moon
OL,9,Fbeing played as a tribute to his late
OL,10,Ffriend Ricky Hatton before he put on a
OL,11,Fshow by dancing on stage while
OL,12,Ffireworks and flames went off around
OL,13,Fhim.
OL,15,FThe pyrotechnics ended there as once
OL,16,Fthe action got underway Makhmudov
OL,17,Fadvanced with crude, one-dimensional
OL,18,Fattacks that Fury appeared to easily
OL,19,Fevade.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
