PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776038571
OL,3,CTyson Fury wins comeback fight against
OL,4,CArslanbek Makhmudov by unanimous
OL,5,Cdecision
OL,7,FThere was plenty of respect between
OL,8,Fthe rivals as they touched gloves at
OL,9,Fthe end of each round and even during
OL,10,Fthe rounds, but as the halfway stage
OL,11,Fcame, it was becoming increasingly one-
OL,12,Fsided.
OL,14,FThe eighth round proved to be Fury's
OL,15,Fstrongest, as he landed telling blows
OL,16,Fthat troubled Makhmudov, including
OL,17,Fsharp right uppercuts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
