OL,5,Cdecision
OL,7,FFury and Joshua exchanged words after
OL,8,Fthe fight with 'The Gypsy King'
OL,9,Fcalling out his rival from the ring
OL,10,Fupon grabbing the microphone, with
OL,11,FJoshua replying "I'll tell you when
OL,12,FI'm ready".
